{"members":[{"header_text":" فس،  [تفسير  القمي ] : ","body_text":"قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَي: <quranic_text>«فِي عِزَّةٍ وَ شِقٰاقٍ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[ص۲]</footnote> يَعْنِي فِي كُفْرٍ قَوْلُهُ: <quranic_text>«فَنٰادَوْا وَ لاٰتَ حِينَ مَنٰاصٍ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[ص۳]</footnote> اَيْ لَيْسَ هُوَ وَقْتَ مَفَرٍّ قَوْلُهُ: <quranic_text>«اِلاَّ اِخْتِلاٰقٌ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[ص۷]</footnote> اَيْ تَخْلِيطٌ قَوْلُهُ: <quranic_text>«مِنَ الْاَحْزٰابِ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[ص۱۱]</footnote> يَعْنِي الَّذِينَ تَحَزَّبُوا عَلَيْكَ يَوْمَ الْخَنْدَقِ.","translation":"","aligned_body":"قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَي TAG_OPEN:quranic_text فِي عِزَّةٍ وَ شِقٰاقٍ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote ص ۲ TAG_CLOSE:footnote يَعْنِي فِي كُفْرٍ قَوْلُهُ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text فَنٰادَوْا وَ لاٰتَ حِينَ مَنٰاصٍ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote ص ۳ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اَيْ لَيْسَ هُوَ وَقْتَ مَفَرٍّّّ قَوْلُهُ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text اِلاَّ اِخْتِلاٰقٌ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote ص ۷ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اَيْ تَخْلِيطٌ قَوْلُهُ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text مِنَ الْاَحْزٰابِ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote ص ۱۱ TAG_CLOSE:footnote يَعْنِي الَّذِينَ تَحَزَّبُوا عَلَيْكَ يَوْمَ الْخَنْدَقِ"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلُهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تعالي","display":"تَعَالَي"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"عزه","display":"عِزَّةٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"شقاق","display":"شِقٰاقٍ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"ص","display":"ص"},{"kind":"word","token":"۲","display":"۲"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"يعني","display":"يَعْنِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"كفر","display":"كُفْرٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلُهُ"},{"kind":"t